room_title: Escape room "The Doctor" by Espionage Escape Rooms in Valparaiso
room_description:
You don’t remember much about last night, just that you went out with your friends, and met a new one. Now, you have all awoken to find yourself cuffed to an operating table! Perhaps the new friend you made last night isn’t so friendly after all! He said he was a Doctor… Dr. Victor Frankenstein.
What does he have in store for you? You must escape his lab before he returns, and destroy his diabolical research to save others from sharing your possible fate!
